  "steps": [
    "Heat oil in a non-stick kadai, add cumin seeds and once they start to change colour, add garlic and green chillies, mix and sauté for 30 seconds.",
    "Add onions, mix and sauté till golden brown. Add tomato puree and salt, mix well, cover and cook till oil separates.",
    "Add red chilli powder, turmeric powder, coriander powder and cumin powder and mix well.",
    "Add ½ cup water and mix well. Add cashewnut paste and mix well.",
    "Add cooked green gram, garam masala powder, kasoori methi powder and coriander leaves and mix well. Add 1 cup water, mix, cover and cook for 4-5 minutes.",
    "Transfer into a serving bowl, garnish with coriander sprig and serve hot with paranthas."
